com.interpss.dc.algo

Interface PVDcPowerFlowAlgorithm

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DcPowerFlowAlgorithm, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PVDcPowerFlowAlgorithmImpl

    public interface PVDcPowerFlowAlgorithm
extends DcPowerFlowAlgorithm
    A representation of the model object 'PV Dc Power Flow Algorithm'. Dc system Loadflow algorithm implementation.

    The following features are supported:

    • Mppt Optimization
    • Mppt Bus
    • Max MPPT Points
    • Mppt Step
    See Also:
    DcSysAlgorithmPackage.getPVDcPowerFlowAlgorithm()
